g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你要幾時去? 你唔經香港球迷會買?<br />\nB級賽事 主場 99.9% 有飛喎(雖然西位)<br />\n之前去朝聖都係經佢地買<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n26號想買我地對李城 第一次去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果一個人去, 就直接英國官網買, 睇下球迷區Stretford end仲有無位<br />\n如果唔係就跟球迷會啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1LJUfqCEtBvWK2IzMLOK9DpaZhniIWThR_mBHZ2UWA3o/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1LJUfqCEtBvWK2IzMLOK9DpaZhniIWThR_mBHZ2UWA3o%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=ZSRyuWgCKr%2F2be2imoqQs8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=b7235fa8\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1LJUfqCEtBvWK2IzMLOK9DpaZhniIWThR_mBHZ2UWA3o/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n我早幾日打既買飛心得 睇下幫唔幫到手 仲未打完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知幾時先有機會去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d555af753e2c425d12180377d7a7a00ee29e67a7","tid":329094,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T05:52:29.000Z","msg":"師奶唔使學體位？"},{"pid":"977dbd88acad04d91fabfe7c9c129cde5f071e0a","tid":329094,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T05:58:50.000Z","msg":"呢條女都OK正"},{"pid":"76eb682535454667baaa75d370f01ea3f7b346dd","tid":329094,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T05:59:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/500/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/20/133559_a39811866ef8520b86222322f0cb32ba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F20%2F133559_a39811866ef8520b8622232